## **Featured Product**

![](https://www.pantone.com/media/catalog/product/p/3/p3d65840-pantone-color-evaluation-3-bulb-light-viewing-booth-product-1_3.jpg?auto=webp&format=pjpg&quality=85)

### PANTONE LIGHT BOOTH

Colors can look different under different lighting conditions outside in daylight, inside retail stores or in your home. Pantone Light Booths are just the tools to make sure you see colors in the best possible light literally! Light booths can be purchased in either a 5-light or 3-light configuration with either a D50 bulb option or a D65 bulb option.

